Company Profile


Loral Space & Communications is a leading space and communications company that has built a record of success in the global satellite industry. Loral owns 62.7% of Telesat, which provides reliable and secure satellite-delivered communications solutions to broadcast, telecom, corporate and government customers on a global basis.

