Careers at Loral


Consider a career with Loral Space & Communications as an exciting, challenging and rewarding opportunity. Loral maintains an entrepreneurial environment in which performance is measured by financial, technical and business achievements, and by rewarding good performance with attractive incentives and competitive benefits.
Loral's corporate headquarters are located in midtown Manhattan. The New York office employs individuals with specialties in finance and accounting, communications, human resources, law, and other professional and technical areas.
For information about employment opportunities in the New York office, contact Daniel Medina, Director of Administrative Services, at (212) 697-1105.
























