	Loral Space & Communications Inc. - Home



































Skip to main content




























































A leading satellite communications services provider and the fourth largest FSS operator in the world.





First commercial satellite operator providing services in the X-band frequency.














Company Profile


Loral Space & Communications is a leading space and communications company that has built a record of success in the global satellite industry. Loral owns 62.7% of Telesat, which provides reliable and secure satellite-delivered communications solutions to broadcast, telecom, corporate and government customers on a global basis.

Learn More







Leadership


Loral's business is managed by a knowledgeable and seasoned team of executives

Meet our leadership team




